channel.title: [194]Project OS - Osiris
channel.description:
[img]http://img823.imageshack.us/img823/4526/cooltext734269041.png[/img]
[font=verdana][size=13px]This thread is about recreating a RS-2 Beta. This is not an attempt to make a RS-2 Beta remake, this is only a project I'm working on for fun. There's alot of work to be done, so wish me good luck.[/size][/font]
Hello. [b]Yeah I've decided to come back[/b], and this time, again with a [b]194[/b] Project. I've decided to continue my old 194 project . I've been looking around on MoparScape and decided to come back, since I can't sleep at night and I don't have nothing to do, I've decided to make a project. I'll be doing my best, and I guess you'll guys support me. [hr] It's not a remake or anything close to it, I'll just be doing the best I can. At the start I'll be working on a Look-a-like until I find a real 194 cache. I'll be asking a few friends if they want to join me, so we'll have more fun and stuff.
Features:
[ul][li][font=verdana][font=Verdana][size=13px]Pickup (the pickup dupe needs to be fixed though)[/size][/font][/font][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Banking[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Dropping[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Leveling up[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Leveling up interfaces, sending the correct chatbox interfaces and messages[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Skill experience[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Bones burying[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Emotions[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Graphics with almost all gfx's working[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Animations with starting and stopping[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Animations aren't being played for only 0.5 seconds, works perfectly[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Game interfaces[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Chat bar interface support[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Item class supporting item and object creating[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Textures renaming[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]A lovely welcome screen, old school one though[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]The client class has been cleaned alot[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]Woodcutting base, not finished[/font][/size][/li] [li][size=13px][font=verdana]NPC system implemented[/font][/size][/li] [li][font=verdana][size=13px]Running almost finished[/size][/font][/li][/ul] [img]http://img207.imageshack.us/img207/203/loginscreen.png[/img]
[img]http://img717.imageshack.us/img717/7613/194fally.png[/img]
[img]http://img407.imageshack.us/img407/2033/pvpsystem.png[/img]
Wanna be in the team? Send me a message.Credits: [ul][li]Blakeman[/li] [li]Diego(me)[/li] [li]Native^[/li] [li]Purely Chill[/li][/ul]
